        </div>
        <div class="panel-body">
          <p><b>Marineda City</b></p>
          <p>Huge shopping center with a variety of Spanish shops.  Also includes a movie theater, a go-kart course and a mini-golf course.  Located in the newer part of the city it can be reached by public bus or taxi.</p>
          <br>
          <p><b>Calle Real</b></p>
          <p>Calle Real is one of the oldest shopping streets in La Coruña.  It includes a wide array of stores, though tends to skew to more upscale shops in recent years.  It is located in the old city and is easily walkable from Plaza Maria Pita.</p>
          <br>
          <p><b>El Corte Ingles</b></p>
          <p>Located by the train and bus station, this shopping center is the equivalent to Spanish Macy's.</p>
        </div>
